{"tid":625744,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"☆★☆★☆稀有! 5種不被國際貓協認可的貓品種☆★☆★☆","createTime":"2018-04-11T16:45:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T08:57:58.000Z","uid":181662,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7e4e94f57fcd12755884222a945ed1bcdcca015d","tid":625744,"uid":181662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T16:45:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\">1. 歐斯亞史烈斯貓 (Ojos Azules)<br />\n<br />\n這是仍屬於新品種的歐斯亞史烈斯貓，最具魅力的地方是，不論是何種被毛，四肢和尾端都是白色，這種貓的深藍色眼珠，不論是何種被毛都有可能出現，在日本也開始漸次受到養貓人士的青睞。體格健壯而含有泰國貓血統，體型則屬於其間。<br />\n<br />\n這種家貓在西班牙語中意為「藍眼睛」，1984年首次在墨西哥被發現，是一種非常罕見的品種 - 在1992年，全世界只有10隻Ojos Azules！</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/12/001536_fac371685b1ebdab752721fded41217b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F12%2F001536_fac371685b1ebdab752721fded41217b.jpg&h=df6bd96b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">2. 肯尼亞貓 (Sokoke Forest Cat)<br />\n<br />\n20世紀70年代，一位生活在肯尼亞的英國婦女JENI SLATER收養了一隻雌貓和它的小貓，後來這些貓成了Sokoke的鼻祖。JENI的一位朋友，加拿大土著CLORIA MOLDRUP後來將兩隻小貓帶回丹麥並於1980年開始定期改良計劃。所有的貓都來源於JENI SLATER的貓屋。MOLDRUP和其他育種專家一起開始了一項育種計劃。<br />\n<br />\n這隻野生貓在1978年在肯雅被發現，並以它首先被發現的森林命名。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/12/002329_2ff4fb7f2af5e45ce49eed10674178e1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F12%2F002329_2ff4fb7f2af5e45ce49eed10674178e1.jpg&h=390d816e&s={SIZE}\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">4. 狼貓 (Lykoi)<br />\n<br />\n美國田納西州（Tennessee）有貓隻配種員利用 Sphinx 無毛貓、短毛貓配種出一種名為「Lykoi」（希臘語）的貓種。「Lykoi」意為「狼貓」（wolf cat）。<br />\n<br />\n首批 Lykoi 共有十四隻，牠們眼睛、鼻子、耳朵均沒有毛，長相有點像《變種特攻》內的「狼人」盧根，但牠們的性格卻似獵狗，喜歡追蹤獵物，性格剛烈、友好和忠誠。遇上陌生人時會起戒心，主人與牠們混熟後，小貓隨即變得友善和忠於主人。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/12/003747_c8f44209ccf451779698d99ceb2123ed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F12%2F003747_c8f44209ccf451779698d99ceb2123ed.jpg&h=1b49898e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">3. 漫切堪貓(Minskin)<br />\n<br />\nMinskin是漫切堪貓（munchkin）與加拿大無毛貓斯芬克斯貓（sphynx）的混種；體形較小，一般在4英鎊，是最小的貓種。<br />\n<br />\n1998年，Paul McSorley開將曼切堪貓與斯芬克斯貓配對進行培育，第一隻Minskin貓在2000年7月出生，它是第一隻培育成功的Minskin貓。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/12/003020_02cd0c10b15ec11fcbd66d6378d3a8a3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F12%2F003020_02cd0c10b15ec11fcbd66d6378d3a8a3.jpg&h=17972b3f&s={SIZE}\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">5. 塞倫蓋蒂貓 (Serengeti)<br />\n<br />\n塞倫蓋蒂貓是孟加拉貓（Bengal）與東方貓（Oriental）的混種。<br />\n<br />\n由加州Kingsmark貓舍的Karen Sausman於1994年所創出。此品種至今仍在發展階段，但最終目的是要創造一種看著起來像藪貓（Serval，非洲山貓）但又不使用任何野生基因的貓種。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/12/002719_e6f57c3f688a9db9dc392f3c10c3e436.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F12%2F002719_e6f57c3f688a9db9dc392f3c10c3e436.jpg&h=8629453a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b314646afab55921e0e08f34619176e0b4e39c44","tid":625744,"uid":78473,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T01:05:04.000Z","msg":"2係唐貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1078a945933041cd3686371857850a2e1f1ca57","tid":625744,"uid":40276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T01:23:10.000Z","msg":"唔認可即係咩意思 即係呢堆唔係屬於貓？定唔養得<br />\n唔明"},{"pid":"d7a8b09bb7c799b90988b62f7d55f158bd86fcf1","tid":625744,"uid":181662,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e1078a945933041cd3686371857850a2e1f1ca57","tid":625744,"uid":40276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T01:23:10.000Z","msg":"唔認可即係咩意思 即係呢堆唔係屬於貓？定唔養得<br />\n唔明"},"citedBy":0,"r